{"tid":2334911,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中資行警告市民: 開離岸戶口小心外國制裁風險","createTime":"2020-12-21T12:33:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T18:06:32.000Z","uid":305299,"like":9,"dislike":130,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"650c38fa327e5e21c4fd573513f631b1eead8a86","tid":2334911,"uid":305299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T12:33:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中產湧美資行   開離岸戶口   部份滙豐客過檔花旗<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201221/KUXRTE4JZBBLJNKAZBS3LZCDCE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201221%2FKUXRTE4JZBBLJNKAZBS3LZCDCE%2F&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzI5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=be9d9db5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201221%2FKUXRTE4JZBBLJNKAZBS3LZCDCE%2F&h=fa4712bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201221/KUXRTE4JZBBLJNKAZBS3LZCDCE/</a><br />\n<br />\n...............<span class=\"red\">中國通海資產管理</span>私人客戶顧問服務總監張佩儀表示，港人在海外開離岸戶口，「可以backup（備案）多個選擇畀自己」，符合分散風險的理財策略，也可能因近期事態發展，市民會考慮除了一貫在本港及內地開戶，不妨在英、美、東南亞等地增設離岸戶口，投放存款、股票、債券、基金或海外物業。但她提醒「唔好人開我又開」，要平衡本身承擔力及閒資多少，隔山買牛要注意外國稅制、保險等營運費，<span class=\"red\">「亦唔排除放錢海外，會突然俾外國制裁的風險。」</span>"},{"pid":"abf8e8ccf9642f16473989943682cb89ab37fb5b","tid":2334911,"uid":83251,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T12:34:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i3bzAkY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi3bzAkY.gif&h=9997a7f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"557e7286aae08c68515e85a2c2cbce83b37c9523","tid":2334911,"uid":47021,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime